metadata.name: Silver Launchpool Labs NFT
metadata.description:
This type of NFT grants Silver membership status for Launchpool Labs allocations.\
        \
         **This NFT does not have tradable value.**\
         \
         Purchasing will be available from the Launchpool team, in OTC manner, with the LPOOL burnt forever.\
         \
         Any purchased NFTs on secondary markets will not grant you access to Launchpool Labs exclusive opportunities.
